Title: Esri Silverlight Wkt Parser
Description: Esri Silverlight Wkt Parser is a refactoring of some SharpMap code.  It supports adds WKT (well known text) geometry parsing to ESRI's Silverlight APIs
HomeWiki:
Project Description
The Esri Silverlight Wkt and Wkb Parser is an Well Known Text / Well Known Binary parser for ESRI's ArcGIS API for Silverlight. It's LGPL licensed, as it is derived from MapSUI / SharpMap.
